casebody.data:
NATIONAL COLLEGIATE ATHLETIC ASSOCIATION, petitioner,
v.
Samuel Michael KELLER, et al. No. 13M54. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 13, 2014.

Motion of A & E Television Networks, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae denied. Motion of National Collegiate Athletic Association for leave to intervene to file a petition for writ of certiorari denied.
